  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dd6\u0db4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0da9\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd3\u00a0\u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9c\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dc4\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two people, including Dhanish Ali, who broke into the television, are banned from traveling abroad",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Chief Magistrate Nandana Amarasinghe ordered today (28) to ban the foreign travel of Roshan Ali Dhanish Ali and Chaminda Calum Priya Amarasinghe in relation to the incident where a group of activists broke into the National Television Corporation and threatened the staff including journalists and joined a live television program.",
        "The magistrate also directed the court registrar to inform the immigration controller of this order.",
        "The magistrate issued this order after taking into consideration the request made by the Kuruduwatta police to ban the travel of the two of them abroad as the above named persons have been identified as suspects in relation to this incident.",
        "The court ordered the prison to present Roshan Ali Dhanish Ali, who was arrested and remanded in custody on a warrant, to the court on the first day of next day and canceled the suspect's identification parade.",
        "The magistrate canceled the identification parade stating that there is no need to conduct the identification parade due to the publication of photos and videos of the suspect in the media."
      ],
